Configuration for SD simulation using an ideal array and
(hypothetical) staions at 1000m from shower axis.

bootstrap.xml.in       Simulates WCD stations with Unified Board (UB)
                       electronics
bootstrap_ssd.xml.in   Simulates WCD+SSD stations with Upgraded 
                       Unified Board (UUB) electronics

Please consult the doxygen-generated documentation for details on how to inspect the configuration files
used for this application.
